FBIS3-22066 "jptdd013__l94069" JPRS-tdd-94-013-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 23 March 1994 NEAR EAST & SOUTH ASIA EGYPT Paint Merchant Caught With 1 Kg of Heroin NC2303213594 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1835 GMT 23 Mar 94 NC2303213594 Cairo MENA Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Cairo, 23 Mar (MENA)--The drug fighting department of the Cairo Security Directorate today caught a paint merchant in the Abu al-'Ila area with 1 kg of pure heroin worth 1.5 million pounds in his possession. Defendant Rushdi 'Abd-al-Hamid Abu-al-Makarim confessed to the prosecution that he bought the heroin through a merchant in the Red Sea area to market it in Cairo.
